A California mother is facing murder charges after she allegedly stabbed her three young daughters to death while her mother was at home and her husband out front working on his car.Â 

Carol Coronado, 30, was found in bed with the bloody bodies of her children, aged three, two and two months old, on Tuesday evening near Torrance in Los Angeles County, according to police.

Police said that she was naked and holding a knife after reportedly trying to cut her own wrists.

Detectives said on Wednesday that there were several knives recovered at a bloody scene.

