Ms Madrid said the children's grandmother told her that the woman had called earlier in the day and said that she was going crazy. The grandmother had stopped by to visit her grandchildren.

Carol Coronado, 30, was arrested on suspicion of murder, taken to a hospital for examination and then to a sheriff's station for booking. Authorities say she made no statement.

